sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Client as Cliente (SPA)
    participant Ctrl as AppointmentController
    participant UC as CreateAppointmentUseCase
    participant Repo as PgAppointmentRepository
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (DB)
    participant Notifier as AppointmentStatusNotifier
    participant Obs as AppointmentStatusEmailObserver
    participant Mail as EmailNotification (Nodemailer)

    Client->>Ctrl: POST /api/v1/appointments (providerId, serviceId, startsAt)
    Ctrl->>Ctrl: Validar payload com Zod
    Ctrl->>UC: execute(input)
    UC->>Repo: findConflict(providerId, startsAt, endsAt)
    Note over Repo, DB: Iniciado locking transacional com SELECT ... FOR UPDATE
    Repo->>DB: Query de concorrência com LOCK
    DB-->>Repo: Retorna conflitos (se houver)
    alt Sem Conflitos
        UC->>Repo: save(appointment)
        Repo->>DB: INSERT INTO appointments
        DB-->>Repo: Confirmado
        UC->>Notifier: publish(statusChangeEvent)
        Notifier->>Obs: update(statusChangeEvent)
        Obs->>Mail: send(recipientEmail, message)
        Note over Mail: Disparo assíncrono em background
        UC-->>Ctrl: Retorna Appointment criado
        Ctrl-->>Client: 201 Created (Appointment JSON)
    else Com Conflito
        DB-->>UC: Conflito detectado (ou exceção de LOCK)
        UC-->>Ctrl: Lança erro (SlotConflictException)
        Ctrl-->>Client: 409 Conflict / Error JSON
    end
